nodes.text: 090192 was a spy ship used by the Confederacy of Independent Systems during the Clone Wars against the Galactic Republic. During the war, the T-series military strategic analysis and tactics droid TX-532 utilized the starship for a secret operation on Naboo.
090192 was mentioned in Rise of the Separatists, a roleplaying supplementary sourcebook for the Star Wars Roleplaying series that was published by Fantasy Flight Games in 2019.
